      <title>新加坡 2023 年最大的房地产交易因监管障碍而失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/singapore-s-largest-property-deal-of-2023-falls-apart-on-regulatory-snag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，一位中国大宗商品亿万富翁支持的一项以约 9.08 亿新元（合 6.71 亿美元）购买新加坡黄金购物区购物中心的重磅交易因当局拒绝重建计划而失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/singapore-s-largest-property-deal-of-2023-falls-apart-on-regulatory-snag</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 08:24:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员正在为 5% 的收益率、不降息的世界做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/bond-traders-shift-thinking-to-a-5-yield-no-rate-cut-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储今年不降息的可能性越来越大，债券交易员正在为 10 年期美国国债收益率突破 5% 做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/bond-traders-shift-thinking-to-a-5-yield-no-rate-cut-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:40:52 GMT</pubDate>
